Version 0.11.1
-------------
 09/12/2009
-------------
Marcio Moreno (marcio@telemidia.puc-rio.br)
-------------

Description:
- Offering an option to build the project with or without the component support.
- New Ginga parameters (type ginga --help for details):
     --device-class
     --disable-gfx
     --enable-automount
     --enable-remove-oc-filter 
     --set-*
     --insert-*

